description: The latest proposal includes a 35% general wage increase over four years — bringing it closer to the union's original ask for 40%. Boeing previously offered a 25% raise over the life of the contract.
title: Boeing union is set to vote on a new contract deal, possibly ending strike

description: The Israeli government said a drone targeted the prime minister’s house, though there were no casualties, as Iran’s supreme leader vowed Hamas would continue its fight.
title: Israel says drone targets Benjamin Netanyahu’s house; strikes in Gaza kill 50

description: The U.S. government's road safety agency is investigating Tesla's “Full Self-Driving” system after getting reports of crashes in low-visibility conditions, including one that killed a pedestrian.
title: U.S. to probe Tesla's 'Full Self-Driving' system after pedestrian killed
